  itemName: The Fridig Dead
  itemDescription: "Upon killing an Enemy affected by Freeze, release 3 skulls that
    last 12 seconds. The skull will follow and attack targets dealing small damage
    and adding a stack of <style=Me>Soul Debt</style>. <style=Me>Soul Debt</style>
    stores damage dealt to the target, after 5 seconds or when the target dies, cause
    a <style=Me>4m</style> explosion dealing <style=Me>60%</style> of the stored
    damage. \r\n\r\n<style=Fine><style=FMe>+0.5m</style> Radius per subsequent stack.\n<style=FMe>+15%</style>
    Damage per subsequent stack.</style>"
